name: Origin
description:
"It was a tiny spark. A spark of intelligence, of life, of beauty. All energies that were part of its once infinite being had been cast off. In isolation it roamed in an endless void, waiting for the day it would no longer be alone." - Sykcolo / AI

Origin by @Sykcoloart

Taking something that most would consider ugly or repulsive and showing it in a different way that transforms it into something uniquely beautiful is the main passion behind this project that I called Metamorphoses.

This artwork is created using generative techniques to mutate and deconstruct a micrograph of a moth wing. 

Learn about the inspiration, story and techniques behind this project on my website: https://www.sykcolo.com/blog-1/the-metamorphoses-collection
